data.description: Well cared for, nicely updated cottage with a lovely water view and your own dock! Enjoy the quiet backyard with landscaped patio area and privacy fence. The perfect resort home or rental with space for a second bedroom presently used as a den. Large walk-in closet with built-ins, laundry room, carport. Quick access though the Marco River to the Gulf. Watch the boats go by from your screened front porch. Fresh exterior paint, main bath remodel, new luxury vinyl floors, range & hot water heater 2022 and new roof 2019. The small island of Goodland has 2 county parks, 2 marinas, several great restaurants and fantastic access to the 10,000 Islands & Everglades for fishing and pristine beaches. Floor plan available.
